02:53.658 --> 03:00.270
Now there's an invitation to every one of us to enjoy the wonders and the pleasures of the great American outdoors.

03:01.051 --> 03:03.416
But that invitation carries with it a little plea.

03:04.538 --> 03:06.621
That we be careful with fire.

03:06.641 --> 03:08.064
Always.

03:08.084 --> 03:16.459
