05:44.433 --> 05:48.859
when you're driving along some country road or through the forest.

05:48.879 --> 05:49.460
See what I mean?

05:50.642 --> 05:54.588
Let's spread the good habits and lock up the bad ones once and for all.

05:55.729 --> 05:59.856
That way we can put an end to man-caused forest fires in this country.

06:01.057 --> 06:10.491
We'll be hearing from Smokey Bear soon on the same subject, but in the meantime, I'm sure we can count on the sons of the pioneers to help us in this fight against forest fires.

06:10.792 --> 06:12.154
Can't we, boys?

06:12.174 --> 06:14.797
Ah, you don't need to worry none about us, Billy.

06:14.817 --> 06:18.342
We're the carefulest fellows with fire when we're out that you ever saw.

06:19.183 --> 06:20.024
You bet.

06:20.425 --> 06:23.129
We break every match we use into little pieces.

06:23.149 --> 06:25.011
That way we make sure it's out cold.

06:25.652 --> 06:29.437
