09:29.242 --> 09:34.206
Drown your campfire with water, then stir it and drown it again.

09:35.307 --> 09:43.074
Four, find out all you can about your local and state laws before you use fire outdoors.

09:43.995 --> 09:45.776
That's how you can help, folks.

09:46.757 --> 09:48.138
It's up to you.

09:49.399 --> 09:52.041
Well, I'll be seeing you.

